data.title: Faye is GREAT!
data.text: I eat here almost every week. My food is always hot and fresh. The breakfast menu is so good. Please try the Pancake Plate. The lunch menu is also great. A nice local place to eat Downtown. Just regular New Orleans food at a great.

data.title: Decent breakfast
data.text:
They make big and good sausage and egg biscuits about as fast as any factory.
Service is good but place is a dive. Somewhat dirty and ran down.
But something must be right about it, they grind out breakfasts all morning without many breaks.

data.title: Del montón...
data.text: Un lugar que se nota que tiene mucha rotación y todo es fresco, pero si uno es un poco exigente con la limpieza la va a pasar mal. Está bueno para desayunar a la pasada sin prestarle mucha atención a nada, pero no para ir especialmente.
